<plot>Chris lives with his father Arnold. One day he wakes up to find a note slid under his closet door. He soon begins experiencing strange things, odd visions, eerie sounds, and a picture of someone familiar to him appearing in his room. His father doesn't believe a word he's saying. As time goes by the visions and sounds become more intense. He soon finds out that whatever is responsible for this is trying to tell him something.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?012647</url></doc>
